title: Boys soccer roundup: Ashong, Pogyo lead Arlington to win
text: Boys soccer roundup: Ashong, Pogyo lead Arlington to win Staff reports 2:04 a.m. EDT October 9, 2015 Arlington's Juan Lavariega (17) tries to control a pass as he takes a foot to the face from Mahopac's Paul Magnesio (3) during a boys soccer game at Mahopac High School Oct. 8, 2015. Arlington won the game. Frank Becerra Jr./The Journal News From left, Arlington's A.J. Ramputi (7) and Mahopac's Christian Shkreli (7) battle for ball control during a boys soccer game at Mahopac High School Oct. 8, 2015. Arlington won the game. Frank Becerra Jr./The Journal News Arlington defeated Mahopac in a boys soccer game at Mahopac High School Oct. 8, 2015.
